@node features "Syndicate Pro Features"
Features:
---------

	o Quite Small (less than 140k uncrunched!)
	o Fast (Negates You From Checking Syndicate Members No.s)
	o Accurate (On going tests from beta testers say'100% reliability')
	o Uses friendly GUI for quick use
	o PD Release Beta Version is crippled (See Intro)
	o ASCII File Format - Users Can Develop There Own Editers!
	o Updated Regularly To Include Bug Fixes,Requests etc (esp E-mail)
	o Forecast/History/Other Options.
	o Only Costs 5 UK pounds
	o Works On accellerated machines*



